<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人望眼欲穿的煙火大會開始囉！<pageBreak />讓我們一起來<delay20 />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />留下美好的回憶吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
你快看！<10_4 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />不是看我，是看煙火～
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的煙火<delay20 />真的十分美麗呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />心靈彷彿受到了洗滌，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得發射如此大量煙火到空中，<delay20 />
是一件很辛苦的事情喔。<pageBreak />所以我們得盡情地<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />享受煙火才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能夠和<tag a="110" b="4" />
一起看煙火，<delay8 />
我感到很開心喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">預～備～<delay20 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />哇～煙火～！<size value="100" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />氣氛開始熱鬧起來了！<delay frames="40" />
我也忍不住大聲喊出來了呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />的煙火<delay8 />
原來這麼漂亮啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我能住在這座島上<delay20 />
真的太好了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我本來還在思考，<delay8 />
要如何用點心<delay20 />來比喻這些
點綴夜空的煙火<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但看著看著，<delay8 />便覺得
比起這些事情，<delay20 />還是享受
當下的煙火最重要！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />我很享受煙火喔～<size value="100" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />我想會被煙火的聲響蓋過，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以就大聲喊出來了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是這一刻<delay8 />
能永遠持續下去就好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，<delay20 />只要一想到
大會馬上就要結束了，<delay8 />
便不禁變得有些多愁善感，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會<delay8 />也差不多接近尾聲了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了不留下遺憾，<delay20 /><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得將這景象
好好地烙印在腦海中才行，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚的煙火看起來特別漂亮<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是因為<tag a="110" b="4" />
在身旁一起觀賞的緣故呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
